 implementation, depending on the dataset. We thus believe that our novel\napproach can have a significant impact on a wide range of text analysis\napplications, forming a promising starting point for deeper natural language\nunderstanding with the Tsetlin Machine.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Sep 2018 16:34:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 16 Sep 2018 21:59:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-18"}
