 away, reaching a signal-to-noise ratio of 5 at 15.7~s after\nthe event starts. This will provide roughly 50.96~s of warning before the\narrival of the first S waves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Sep 2018 05:50:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-14"}
