ems the\nsize dependence is quite irregular, due to variations in level spacings at the\nFermi energy. The fluctuations die out if the gap parameter spans several level\nspacings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Sep 2018 12:43:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Jul 2019 09:03:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-19"}
