lly, it would be helpful in the cases where the target\nnucleus is stable against alpha decay or alpha-decay data are currently not\navailable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Sep 2018 13:41:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-17"}
